{"tid":1450500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林奠嘅劇本 聽日想我地塞港鐵","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:47:54.000Z","uid":80972,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f2fbb2ad652f4731f60c9e99ff60d37e8213e6ba","tid":1450500,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:39:40.000Z","msg":"我有藍絲同事上星期已經話睇到whatsapp話星期一會塞鐵<br />\n明明我日日上連登都冇人提<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">星期一塞鐵一定係林奠嘅劇本</span><br />\n<br />\n我地應該話俾市民知我地今晚有幾嬲!<br />\n唔係要塞鐵，令大家返唔到工，令佢地都嬲示威者。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">係要大家逐步對政權反抗!</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日星期一要令全民免費搭港鐵!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原理係咁<br />\nNetflix 有套Derren Brown: Pushed to the Edge，設計令普通人去殺人就係首先<span style=\"color: orange;\">令佢做d好簡單嘅野，等佢個錯愈來愈多</span>，最後就會聽話去殺人。我地唔係去殺人，但要好多和非再支持我地，就要令佢地更覺得犯法係無野，政權係可以反對!"},{"pid":"e22d2778acff559794f58129f12e6bf0c1eed8e6","tid":1450500,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:40:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dae59fe3d86628340978ceb8dc749694203b098d","tid":1450500,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbee8c0cd07974a1ae7bd7b985136fe955fe936","tid":1450500,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:45:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5794c98841f1a67390a4b61406a035b934d2bd93","tid":1450500,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:47:54.000Z","msg":"推"}]}